defaultString: You may exchange your points for this item.
stringVals: A wieldable ring that can check your task progress. It has 8 charges for teleporting to useful Slayer sites.
Crossbow bolts that can pierce the hides of creatures such as Turoth and Kurasks. Levels 55 Slayer and 61 Ranged required, and a runite crossbow or better.
Arrows that can pierce the hides of creatures such as Turoth and Kurasks. Levels 55 Slayer and 50 Ranged required, and a magic bow or better.
The herb sack has the ability to store up to 30 of each major grimy herb. Requires 58 Herblore to use.
